&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Me is a luminary of Cazic Thule -- some peeples call us Trolls. Me wuz reincarnated in Neriak when dem froggies was doin' renovashun of Grobb, but now mes has returned to da swamp homelan. &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
