&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;B&gt;ooc&lt;/B&gt;: Really, it's Kedge Keep. Yes, I know it doesn't qualify as "land" but that’s really the point, isn't it? I cannot describe my amazement (back 7 years ago) that the engine could handle swimming much less going in all directions much less figuring in a drowning and air pockets. To explore it was truly the greatest challenge of my play characters life and I take immense pride in knowing every twist and turn of that zone. It is an adventurer's paradise. &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;6. What has been your best or favorite moment as a Guide?&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;*picks teeth with bone* I dunno, dat last mud bath was pritty gud. &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
